S.FORM: Maibul i Hualien a kuwan nu Kalinku ku niyazu' nu Maibul. u kasalumaluma' nu Maibul sa, 108 ku luma'. kumud nu kasabinawlan sa, 245 ku tademawan. kasabinawlan nu Ingcumin sa, 180 ku tademaw, pakalatu 73 . u zuma sa, cay ku Ingcumin, 65 ku tademaw, pakalatu 27 . u kasabinacadan, Amis 39 , Bunun 3 , Tayal 4 , Paiwan 1 , Sakizaya 25 , zumazuma 1 . malalitin tu ihekalay atu zumaay a natinengan
